OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fextensively cloudy during the evening
OL,7,Fand overnight, with some low-level
OL,8,Fmist and haze. Cloud may be thick
OL,9,Fenough for the odd spot of drizzle in
OL,10,Fplaces, although staying dry for most.
OL,11,FCloud-cover helping to prevent a
OL,12,Ffrost. Light winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FMurky, with extensive low
OL,15,Fcloud that may bring a little light
OL,16,Frain or drizzle, although some limited
OL,17,Fbrighter intervals may develop later.
OL,18,FMilder than on Saturday for most.
OL,19,FLight winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
